.el .ds Aq '
.TH SM-ENGAGEMENT 1  "engagement " 
.SH NAME
engagement \- Manage engagement status and fields
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBengagement\fR [\fB\-\-status\fR] [\fB\-\-start\-date\fR] [\fB\-\-end\-date\fR] [\fB\-\-credentials\-ready\fR] [\fB\-\-retest\fR] [\fB\-\-from\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIPATH\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage engagement status and fields
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-status\fR \fI<STATUS>\fR
Update engagement status (planned, in_progress, paused, completed, closed)
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
draft
.IP \(bu 2
planned
.IP \(bu 2
in_progress
.IP \(bu 2
paused
.IP \(bu 2
completed
.IP \(bu 2
closed
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-start\-date\fR \fI<START_DATE>\fR
Update start date (YYYY\-MM\-DD)
.TP
\fB\-\-end\-date\fR \fI<END_DATE>\fR
Update end date (YYYY\-MM\-DD)
.TP
\fB\-\-credentials\-ready\fR
Toggle credential readiness
.TP
\fB\-\-retest\fR
Create a retest engagement (use with \-\-from)
.TP
\fB\-\-from\fR \fI<FROM>\fR
Original engagement to copy findings from (for \-\-retest)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIPATH\fR>
Engagement path (client/project/engagement)
